Keyboard Shortcuts which make our work faster

Home - Moves to start of the current
End - Moves to end of the current line
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Arrow keys (Up,Down,Left,Right) - Move the cursor by one character
Shift + Arrow keys - Select the content
Ctrl + Up/Down - Scroll the page
Ctrl + Right/Left - Move the cursor by next/previous word
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Alt + Tab - Switch b/w recent tabs
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ctrl + U - Change case of selected word into lowercase
Ctrl + Shift + U - Change case of selected word into UPPERCASE
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Cursor : 
Single click - Place the cursor
Double click - Select the word
Triple click - Select entire line
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
